===Overview===
The '''New York Knicks''' are an [[American]] professional basketball team based in [[Manhattan]], [[New York City]]. The Knicks compete in the National Basketball Association. The team plays its home games at [[Madison Square Garden]]. They are one of two NBA teams in New York the other being the [[Brooklyn Nets (Earth-616)|Brooklyn Nets]].
